event: response.output_text.done
data: {"type":"response.output_text.done","content_index":0,"item_id":"msg_0e0e00ae26fbcf5c006a0aef1e018c8196a9079eb35c7b940a","logprobs":[],"output_index":0,"sequence_number":180,"text":"One innovative solution for reducing food waste in restaurants is the implementation of a \"Smart Ingredient Inventory System\" (SIIS).\n\n**Idea:** Create a digital system that uses AI and IoT sensors to monitor and manage ingredients in real-time. The system predicts demand based on historical data, weather patterns, local events, and reservation trends. It then automatically adjusts orders to suppliers and suggests daily special menus to optimize the use of near-expiry ingredients. Additionally, it provides insights on portion sizes and customer preferences, helping chefs create more efficient menus.\n\n**Category:** Technology\n\n**Feasibility:** 8\n\n**Resources:** \n1. AI software for data analysis and prediction\n2. IoT sensors for inventory tracking\n3. A digital dashboard interface for restaurant staff\n4. Training programs for staff\n5. Partnership with data analytics firms\n6. Ongoing tech support and maintenance"}

